Pros:. Sound Quality. FM Radio. Adjustable EQ. Voice Recorder. Battery. Simple. 
Cons:. There has never been a single problem outside of the problems I cause.. 
Summary:. Well I have had my Sansa for about a year and a half now. I have a few songs installed that have problems but that is because I had to set them to low quality to lower the space it takes up. That problem is my fault, not the products. Well over this year and a half, I have not had a single problem. It's amazingly compact, easy to use, portable beyond belief, an internal battery that charges easy, and great sound quality. I love the Sansa products and I am planning on buying the 4gb. The 1gb holds everything it says it can but I just have too many songs and too little money to buy a better one currently. My friend has a Zune and another has an iPod touch and they are both impressed by the quality and features provided on my Sansa.. 

