Summary:. I've had many MP3 players over the last 6 years that I use to workout 3-4 times a week and this is by far the best of them.. It sounds better than my old 250$ Samsung Yepp MP3 player, radio reception is better, battery lasts longer and it's super intuitive and easy to use.. Very clear sound: this surprised me a lot as I was expecting worse sound quality than in my previous more expensive and bigger flash MP3 players.. It also fits perfectly in my pocket and enables me to forget it while working out since it also weighs close to nothing.. 

